SQL> -- 7. WAQTD TOTAL SALARY NEEDED TO PAY AND NUMBER OF SALESMAN IN EACH DEPT .
SQL> SELECT SUM(SAL) , COUNT(*)
  2  FROM EMP
  3  WHERE JOB='SALESMAN'
  4  GROUP BY DEPTNO;

  SUM(SAL)   COUNT(*)                                                                                                                                                                                   
---------- ----------                                                                                                                                                                                   
      5600          4                                                                                                                                                                                   

